The theorem statement is:
`theorem findExponents_spec_satisfied (n: Nat) (primes: List Nat) (h_precond : findExponents_precond (n) (primes)) : findExponents_postcond (n) (primes) (findExponents (n) (primes) h_precond) h_precond := by ...`

